ice to the nation he was first awarded India's second highest civilian award, Padma Vibhushan in 2008 and then honored with Bharat Ratna - India's highest civilian award in 2019.","title":"Ex-Indian President Pranab Mukherjee passes away at 84","url":"http://en.setopati.com/political/153798","video":[]}
